## 4. 数据模型关系

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Prompt {
        +String id
        +String userId
        +String title
        +String content
        +String? categoryId
        +List~String~ tags
        +List~Variable~ variables
        +int usageCount
        +DateTime createdAt
        +DateTime updatedAt
        +fromJson()
        +toInsertJson()
    }

    class Category {
        +String id
        +String userId
        +String name
        +String? parentId
        +int sortOrder
        +DateTime createdAt
        +fromJson()
        +toJson()
        +copyWith()
    }

    class Variable {
        +String name
        +String description
        +String? defaultValue
        +fromJson()
        +toJson()
    }

    class CopyHistoryEntry {
        +String promptId
        +String title
        +String content
        +DateTime copiedAt
    }

    Prompt "1" --> "*" Variable : variables
    Category "1" --> "*" Category : parentId
    Category "1" --> "*" Prompt : categoryId
```

