## 5. Supabase 表操作映射

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph AuthProvider
        SignIn[signInWithPassword]
        SignUp[signUp]
        SignOut[signOut]
        Listen[onAuthStateChange]
    end

    subgraph PromptRepository
        FP[fetchPrompts]
        SP[searchPrompts]
        CP[createPrompt]
        UP[updatePrompt]
        DP[deletePrompt]
        IU[incrementUsageCount]
        FC[fetchCategories]
        CC[createCategory]
        UC[updateCategory]
        DC[deleteCategory]
        RC[reorderCategories]
    end

    subgraph AiService
        Opt[optimizePrompt]
    end

    SignIn & SignUp & SignOut --> AuthAPI[auth API]
    Listen --> AuthAPI

    FP & SP & CP & UP & DP & IU --> PromptsTable[prompts 表]
    FC & CC & UC & DC & RC --> CatTable[categories 表]
    Opt --> EdgeFn[optimize-prompt]
```

---

## 6. 依赖层级表

| 层级 | 模块 | 依赖 | 说明 |
|------|------|------|------|
| L1 | `main.dart` | `app.dart`, Provider, Supabase, dotenv | 应用启动与全局注入 |
| L2 | `app.dart` | GoRouter, screens, AuthProvider | 路由定义与主题 |
| L3 | `AuthProvider` | supabase_flutter | 会话状态 |
| L3 | `PromptProvider` | PromptRepository | 业务状态聚合 |
| L4 | screens | Provider, services | UI 与用户交互 |
| L5 | `PromptRepository` | supabase_flutter, models | 数据库 CRUD |
| L5 | `AiService` | supabase_flutter | Edge Function 调用 |
| L5 | `CopyHistoryService` | shared_preferences | 设备本地历史 |
| L6 | models | 无外部业务依赖 | 纯数据结构 |
